# Design Tokens

Source of truth: `design-tokens/` directory. W3C Design Tokens v2025.10 format.

## Rules

- All tokens use `$value` and `$type` (W3C format). Add `$description` for non-obvious tokens.
- Token names map to `--sc-*` CSS custom properties after build.
- After editing any `.tokens.json`, run `cd design-tokens && npm run build`.
- Generated outputs: CSS, Kotlin, Swift, C, Dart. Never hand-edit generated files.
- Reference `docs/design-strategy.md` for design philosophy.
